Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Wow, awesome! Poirot's really in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:10.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A reporter came here a while back and said he was going to publish a piece about us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I never expected that it'd be an article this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're even in there, Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Taii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, a calico cat who frequents the café, and Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a beautiful Poirot employee."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right! She's even holding Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Maybe calling me beautiful is a bit much...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Newspaper articles usually do exaggerate the facts, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing about you, Amuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I happened to be off work that day, because I wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a pity that you missed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially since you're so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, one of the men in black wouldn't exactly want his face showing up in a random gourmet food magazine like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, wasn't there another kid in your group?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did ask her if she wanted to come to Poirot to see Taii...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But apparently she suddenly remembered something she had to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Talking about Taii!! Where is he?! Is he already here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s been staying at my house since last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taii may be a stray cat, but he has a collar, so he must belong to someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still... He's turned up covered in scratches from getting into fights with other cats around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's a photo of him in that magazine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Taii's owner is really searching for him, I'm sure they'll see the article and turn up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's not fair to keep Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's no way his owner would find such a tiny photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe if it was on the Internet, but like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you'd think, right? But we've got a surprise...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the Café Poirot from the magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I read in that article... Apparently a cat turns up in the evenings to beg for food? There was a photo and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:22.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's actually my cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:24.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for him for the last six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you trying to pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:32.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's my family's cat, I know it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't just say something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! The owners really did turn up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And not just one, but two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-They're not the only two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's another one waiting inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.98,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let the refreshing autumn breeze blow away your summer fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:59.28,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Three people claiming to be his owner?!\NTime for a Kogorō and Bourbon deduction tag-team!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.82,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.28,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.41,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! How many times do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:05:00.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This cat is my granddaughter's cat, Mugi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's my Mugi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you bringing her here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I left to go and get him, I bumped into these kids and we got talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then these two men turned up\Nclaiming to be his owners too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm his real owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! I'm telling you, he's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to steal my granddaughter's cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s really popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why do three people want him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just an ordinary calico cat, like you'd see anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not that ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he's certainly a brilliant cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even took your message to this café, back when we were all trapped in that nasty delivery van!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} was really helpful back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in the end, that message just got blown away by the wind when he brought it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, if you would, go home and bring Taii here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While we're waiting, I'll hear\Nwhat each of them have to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...with a mystery-solving specialist at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A mystery-solving specialist?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me he means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Looking for a cat's owner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ask someone else! I'm busy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Goro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's that scary old hag's cat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Scary old hag...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mother{\i0} had to go to Fukuoka for work,\Nso she asked me to look after him for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Off you go, leave! It's not like I'd\Neven be getting paid for it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll hire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For payment, I'll give you a ticket to a premium seat at Yōko Okino's summer concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see, the first cat owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shagawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I hear you're a housewife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just how simple-minded are you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when did your cat go missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked a friend to take care of him since we were going on a family holiday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but apparently he vanished the moment she took her eyes off him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a photo of the cat's owner, my granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it's a photo from five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. He's just a kitten in the photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the markings on his body do look similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See! Even this nice detective agrees with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you like cats too, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, your cat does seem to be quite shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though he certainly loves his owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This cat isn't even mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The calico cat from the café had been neutered, do you know anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was a rough time for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was kept in overnight, and when he came out, he had to keep his bandages on for some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it was a week or so before they took the stitches out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, president of an IT company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're the second candidate for this cat's owner... When did your cat go missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I moved, four months ago now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife of thirty years passed away, so I decided to sell our house and move into a flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sure he was in his carrier when he was put into the moving company's van,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when we came to empty the van, he'd vanished...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any photos of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a photo taken on my phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just the cat and my wife in the photo, but I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This looks just like the Poirot cat too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same cat, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you like cats, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to hold him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you got a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I suppose I must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, was your cat neutered?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my wife handled everything like that, so I don't know the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do remember that despite having surgery, he didn't have any bandages,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but just what looked like a parabolic antenna around his neck though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said... Just bring the cat\Nhere, you'll know soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm his owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, I'd like to hear what happened, part-time worker Amesawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did your cat go missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I value freedom, so I let him roam free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then one day, he suddenly didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any photos of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Course I don't. I value his freedom too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you like cats, right, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! Goro's usually so wary of strangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always got along well with animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then do you remember whether he had been neutered?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows... He was fully grown when I got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and by the way... We've been calling Taii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} "him", but she's actually a girl, you know?{adapted, original: It said "Taii-kun" in the magazine, but he's actually a girl, you know?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then maybe she's not my cat after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taii's a tom cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can even see his balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't scare me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course he's male!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So which of those three is his owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be that young guy, right? Even Goro really liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the photo the other man had looked just like Taii.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he wasn't even in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about the old woman's photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's from when he was a kitten...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you figured anything out, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not quite yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's it! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Turn that down! It's hard to think with that noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Noise...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, right. I should tell Ai{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three owners for Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} turned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:48.47,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Everyone's at their wits' end trying to figure out who's the real owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking about everyone, just Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.73,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What expression's on his face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:59.48,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's got a big, beaming, mischievous smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then everything'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.41,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It seems he's found the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you call us all here because you figured out who his owner was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, as for that, Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} from Poirot should be arriving with the cat any moment now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:27.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well you should've just said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With him here, we can easily tell who the owner is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my cat's owner is my granddaughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? He's obviously my cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But didn't you know that when some cats see three people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they're drawn to the one in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never know, he could've just leapt to you because you were standing in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My cat would've never jumped into the arms of someone as shady as him otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's try it again, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can stand on the left or the right, it won't change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an even better method we can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an experiment that'll let us\Nidentify the owner right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Azusa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taii{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s calmly eating in front of the door to the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then try coming here and opening the door one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One-on-one, he'll be able to identify his owner for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's start with Shagawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, Mugi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, it's me. Don't you recognise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mugi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it won't work unless it's\Nhis owner, my granddaughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he'd do the same thing with your granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, this cat is male, and the\None you're looking for is female.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Amuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shagawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you said that when your cat was neutered, it was hospitalised overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then it was a week until the stitches were removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren't describing a male cat being castrated, but a female cat being spayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spaying is an invasive procedure involving opening up the abdomen and removing the ovaries,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where castration is a simple procedure that just needs the scrotum to be cut open and the testicles removed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so it generally doesn't need a cat to stay overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that's needed to be done post-operation is to make the cat wear a collar so he doesn't lick the wound, like Masuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} described.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:15:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you made it sound like you and your granddaughter lived with the cat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the truth is that she just brought\Nit to visit occasionally, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to know how to act around cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cats don't like being stared at\Nby anyone but their owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why when you were calling Goro to come to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he went to Uncle Kogorō instead, even though he was just ignoring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that what really happened is that your granddaughter had to go away somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and left her cat with you, but she disappeared, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My granddaughter went on a school trip, and her parents decided to go abroad while she was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was asked to take care of her cat, but I couldn't seem to make friends with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then she vanished when I took my eyes off her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do, but then the picture of the cat in the magazine leapt out at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you thought the Poirot cat could replace the cat you were missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But male and female cats even have different body shapes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But my granddaughter gets back from her trip tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to face up to her\Nif I don't figure something out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did she go missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night, after eating dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked everywhere a cat could hide, inbetween the furniture and anything with an opened door,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't find her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you should try searching places behind closed doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Places like toilets, cupboards, and inside washing machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cats can sneak in through doors unnoticed the moment they're opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'll go and have another look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! What a crazy old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you try next, Amesawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just do what Shagawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure! I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though you know how this is going to go already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. It'll be just like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll jump up and start purring, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what's wrong? Jump up here, like before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catnip's effects only last for five to ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with that gone, you're nothing more than a random stranger who's yelling at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just look at Goro if you want proof. He was happily playing with you before, but now he's scared and won't even come near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you were really his owner, you wouldn't need to cover yourself in catnip dust when coming to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I can explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} told you that he was female, you backed off straight away, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd really seen him in the magazine and were convinced enough that he was yours to come all the way here to get him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's no way you'd back down so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was female, he wouldn't have any value at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Value? Isn't he just an ordinary moggy?{...moggy? -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're thinking of female calico cats...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But due to chromosomal abnormalities, only one in a thousand calico cats are male.{one... is -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That rarity is why {\i1}manekineko{\i0} beckoning cats were modelled on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're worth at least a million yen each...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I've heard some have sold\Nfor twenty million yen or more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Twenty million yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As rare as a white lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just how many eel lunches is that, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obviously, someone like you who knows how rare they are wouldn't let such a rare cat run wild in such a big city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm sorry for wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now finally, why don't you try, Masuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's been four months... And my wife usually gave him his food...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll probably go just like with those other two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sōseki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you do remember me, Sōseki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was waiting there even before the door was opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw on TV that cats have great hearing, and they always remember the sound of their owner's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, you said he vanished when you were moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you have the Cheetah Moving Centre handle your move?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. But how did you know that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's climbed into the back of a delivery van belonging to that company before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to be reunited with his owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've thought he could get home if he went in a van with the same logo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm happy for you, Tai{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-chan{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Tai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't run away again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has my address and e-mail on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we can arrange a time, I'd be happy for you to come and visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, I never knew cats were drawn to the person standing in the middle of a group...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he hadn't said that, he wouldn't have had a chance to do the experiment with the footsteps, so he had to tell that little fib.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's got sharp claws hiding under that innocent smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, since we were talking about cats...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a pun, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:32.24,Signs,,0,0,0,,One Week Later
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:32.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I never thought that old man would be the one to contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The e-mail he sent to the detective agency said we could come today if we wanted to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only been a few days since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he decided to get rid of his cat after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seemed to be allergic to cats...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Allergic to cats...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though he owns one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, some people get cats without ever knowing they're allergic to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and some people develop allergies\Nto them while owning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then that means he's gonna sell it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twenty million yen {\i1}is{\i0} hard to refuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:10.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't that Masuko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please open the door!\NI heard a strange noise from in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! It's the caretaker! Are you okay in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this cat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this cat doesn't look injured at all, but there's blood on its paws...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But then that must mean that Masuko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:39.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's blood on his paws!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something must've happened inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do any of you have a string or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:54.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it the room at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you two don't have time to be fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:05.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's tape and scissors here, but the bin is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:08.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why isn't it anywhere here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: The Case of the Beckoning Calico Cat (Part II)!
